{"type":"article","id":3386,"title":"近期中共军方针对香港的集结动向汇总（大家把相关内容都回复到本帖）","uid":1,"topics":[2494,2143,2601,1541,17],"contents":"【报道】<br>\nGuardian<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/aug/13/colour-revolution-jibe-implies-china-will-stop-at-little-to-crush-hong-kong-protests\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">China flaunts military muscle as it seeks to quell Hong Kong's ‘colour revolution’&nbsp;</a><br>\nRFA<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/shenzhen-08152019083824.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">大批武警军事屯驻深圳湾体育馆　美媒指无迹象进香港</a><br>\nHK01<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/364223/%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E6%95%B8%E7%99%BE%E8%A3%9D%E7%94%B2%E8%BB%8A-%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%83%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%BA%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E7%81%A3%E6%BC%94%E7%BF%92-%E8%BB%8D%E5%AA%92%E6%9B%BE%E7%A8%B1%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%8F%AF%E8%B5%B4%E6%B8%AF\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">HK01</a>相关报道<br>\n<br>\n【照片】<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190816210628/https://club.6parkbbs.com/military/index.php?app=forum&amp;act=threadview&amp;tid=15333601\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">照片显示深圳体育馆集结，</a><br>\n<b>美联社：卫星照片显示大批军用车辆深圳集结</b><br>\n送交者: <a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190816210628/https://home.6park.com/index.php?app=home&amp;act=chatnew&amp;uname=NTA2NTQwOTQ%3D\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">shing</a>[大司徒★★★★☆] 于 2019-08-16 2:13 已读 1073 次 1 赞<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/3eq0RvW.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3eq0RvW.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/3eq0RvW.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190816210628im_/https://www.popo8.com/host/data/201908/16/8/0db9723.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190816210628im_/https://www.popo8.com/host/data/201908/16/8/0db9723.jpg\" alt=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190816210628im_/https://www.popo8.com/host/data/201908/16/8/0db9723.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></center><br>\n6park.com<br>\n<br>\n香港反修订《逃犯条例》的示威持续，继中国大陆媒体早前报道有大批武警车队在深圳集结后，美联社昨天（14日）报道，据8月12日的卫星图片显示，超过500辆怀疑是武警装甲运兵车和其他车辆停泊在深圳湾体育中心，相信与近日香港局势有关。<br>\n美联社报道，两张由Maxar's WorldView在8月12日拍摄的卫星图片显示，包括中国武警部队运兵车在内的超过500辆车辆，停泊在深圳湾体育中心。而深圳湾体育中心的位置，接近接驳香港的深圳湾口岸。<br>\n<br>\n另据法新社今天报道，数千名武警在深圳体育馆内演练，体育场外也也集结数十辆装甲车及卡车。 6park.com<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<center><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190816210628im_/https://www.popo8.com/host/data/201908/16/8/3378642.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190816210628im_/https://www.popo8.com/host/data/201908/16/8/3378642.jpg\" alt=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190816210628im_/https://www.popo8.com/host/data/201908/16/8/3378642.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></center><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ll9FtnX.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ll9FtnX.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ll9FtnX.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n深圳湾体育中心停放大批军用车辆。（路透社）<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/nA9YDJZ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nA9YDJZ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/nA9YDJZ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190816210628im_/https://www.popo8.com/host/data/201908/16/8/f7f8af3.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190816210628im_/https://www.popo8.com/host/data/201908/16/8/f7f8af3.jpg\" alt=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190816210628im_/https://www.popo8.com/host/data/201908/16/8/f7f8af3.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></center><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/dTmH1db.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dTmH1db.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/dTmH1db.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n深圳湾体育中心停放大批军用车辆。（路透社） 6park.com<br>\n<br>\n<center><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190816210628im_/https://www.popo8.com/host/data/201908/16/8/b8e82fb.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190816210628im_/https://www.popo8.com/host/data/201908/16/8/b8e82fb.jpg\" alt=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190816210628im_/https://www.popo8.com/host/data/201908/16/8/b8e82fb.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></center><br>\n<br>\n圳湾体育中心停放大批军用车辆。（法新社） <br>\n中国大陆媒体昨天曾广泛转发解放军东部战区微信的图片，显示大量军车停泊在深圳湾体育中心，并表示“从这里出发抵达香港只需要10分钟”。<br>\n<br>\n此前，中国媒体在8月12日纷纷专访一则武警车队在深圳集结的视频。《环球时报》总编辑胡锡进表示，这无疑是国家对香港暴力分子的严正警告。若香港继续乱下去，终会走到国家力量直接干预的那一步。<br>\n<br>\n多维新闻<br>\n<a href=\"http://photo.dwnews.com/mil/photo/2019-08-15/60145405.html#p=1\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://photo.dwnews.com/mil/photo/2019-08-15/60145405.html#p=1</a><br>\n<br>\n【地图】<br>\n深圳湾体育馆位置<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/KBczeU0.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KBczeU0.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/KBczeU0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n驻港部队分布<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/7ZBn8az.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7ZBn8az.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/7ZBn8az.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-08-16","agreeCount":5,"discussionCount":0}